<p>'This is what's happening guys. My new name is Emmy Ma. Ask about me. I have the dopest friends. This is a thing that's happening. And I told you I was getting a red carpet!'</p>

<p>The George Washington University grad - who vows to remain a virgin until marriage - was sad her parents could not be with her but they only landed in the States on Sunday.</p>

<p>Yvonne famously scored the role of Issa Dee's (Issa Rae) promiscuous lawyer best friend Molly Carter in Insecure without an agent or any real acting experience.</p>

<p>HBO officially renewed Insecure for a fifth season in May, and the cast reunited virtually last Wednesday for the first table read.</p>

